    "This narrow bandwidth greatly enhances subsequent processing efficiency.",
    "As part of the successive stages of processing, the IF signal is directed to an analog-to-digital converter (ADC) with a sampling rate of 2 MHz and a resolution of 12 bits.",
    "For more information on the chipset hardware, the reader can refer to [23,24].Further, as shown in Fig. 1(b), the radar system incorporates three receiving antennas arranged in an L-shaped configuration.",
    "As a result, the received IF digital signal from all three receiving antennas encompasses valuable target information, such as range, Doppler, and angles.",
    "These values can be estimated through additional utilization of digital signal processing algorithms, as will be elaborated in \"Gesture Frame Detection: A Key Step in Data Preprocessing for Training Enhancement\" section."
